Class CVEObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.spnthreatviz.CVEObject

  • public class CVEObject
extends java.lang.Object
    A class representing a single CVE Object, holding all information important for ThreatViz.

      • CVEObject

        public CVEObject()
        Default constructor for the CVEObject class, used when creating an empty instance to be populated with data.

      • CVEObject

        public CVEObject(java.lang.String vendor,
                 java.lang.String productName,
                 java.lang.String[] versionValues,
                 java.lang.String description,
                 java.lang.String attackVector,
                 java.lang.String attackComplexity,
                 java.lang.String privilegesRequired,
                 java.lang.String userInteraction,
                 java.lang.String confidentialityImpact,
                 java.lang.String integrityImpact,
                 java.lang.String availabilityImpact,
                 float baseScore,
                 java.lang.String baseSeverity,
                 float exploitabilityScore,
                 float impactScore,
                 java.lang.String publishDate,
                 java.lang.String lastModifiedDate)
        Default constructor for the CVEObject class, used with data provided from JSON.
        Parameters:
        vendor - vendor for the product with the vulnerability.
        productName - product with the vulnerability.
        versionValues - versions of product that contain vulnerability.
        description - description of vulnerability.
        attackVector - attack vector for the vulnerability (baseMetricV3).
        attackComplexity - attack complexity for the vulnerability (baseMetricV3).
        privilegesRequired - Required privileges required to abuse vulnerability (baseMetricV3).
        userInteraction - What type of user interaction is needed to abuse vulnerability (baseMetricV3).
        confidentialityImpact - confidentiality impact of the vulnerability (baseMetricV3).
        integrityImpact - integrity impact of the vulnerability (baseMetricV3).
        availabilityImpact - availability impact of the vulnerability (baseMetricV3).
        baseScore - base score of the vulnerability (baseMetricV3).
        baseSeverity - base severity of the vulnerability (baseMetricV3).
        exploitabilityScore - exploitability score of the vulnerability (baseMetricV3).
        impactScore - impact score of the vulnerability (baseMetricV3).
        publishDate - publishing date of the vulnerability (YYYY-MM-DD).
        lastModifiedDate - last modification date of the vulnerability (YYYY-MM-DD).
